name: Cloud City Engineer
Lore: 'Maintenance specialist Lee Phenets. Assigned to ensure the smooth operation of Cloud City. One of the few humans respected by the city''s Ugnaughts.',
Text: 'When present at a converted site, may use 2 Force to raise your site to the top. Also, when present at an opponent''s site that has a Scomp link, your Force drains are +1 there. Ugnaughts deploy -1 to same Cloud City site.',
